videos.description: After battling back to defeat Illinois in the ReliaQuest Bowl game, No. 22 Bulldogs' coach Zach Arnett praises Mike Leach for putting the right pieces togehter.

videos.headline: MS State rallies to win ReliaQuest Bowl, honors Leach
videos.description: While doing it for Mike Leach, Marcus Banks returns a fumble 60 yards for a TD on the final play as No. 22 MS State rallies to beat Illinois, 19-10.
